verbose_text: Combined over-expression of PIWIL3 and piR-30188 contributed to the attenuation of the proliferation, migration, and invasion of glioma cells while promoting apoptosis, suggesting that piR-30188 was involved in PIWIL3 's regulation of the biological behavior of glioma cells.
